quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,"'uqsim allah taealaa bialmalayikat tasif fi ebadtha sfwfana mtrast, wbalmlaykt tzjr alsahab wtswqh bi'amr allh, wbalmlaykt tatlu dhikr allah wklamh teala. 'iina mebwdkm -ayha alnas- lawahid la sharik lh, fakhlsu lah alebadt waltae. wyqsm allah bima sha' min khlqh, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, falhlf bighayr allah shrk"
  37,2,"aqsm allah taealaa bialmalayikat tasif fi ebadtha sfwfana mtrast, wbalmlaykt tzjr alsahab wtswqh bi'amr allh, wbalmlaykt tatlu dhikr allah wklamh teala. 'iina mebwdkm -ayha alnas- lawahid la sharik lh, fakhlsu lah alebadt waltae. wyqsm allah bima sha' min khlqh, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, falhlf bighayr allah shrk"
  37,3,"aqsm allah taealaa bialmalayikat tasif fi ebadtha sfwfana mtrast, wbalmlaykt tzjr alsahab wtswqh bi'amr allh, wbalmlaykt tatlu dhikr allah wklamh teala. 'iina mebwdkm -ayha alnas- lawahid la sharik lh, fakhlsu lah alebadt waltae. wyqsm allah bima sha' min khlqh, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, falhlf bighayr allah shrk"
  37,4,"aqsm allah taealaa bialmalayikat tasif fi ebadtha sfwfana mtrast, wbalmlaykt tzjr alsahab wtswqh bi'amr allh, wbalmlaykt tatlu dhikr allah wklamh teala. 'iina mebwdkm -ayha alnas- lawahid la sharik lh, fakhlsu lah alebadt waltae. wyqsm allah bima sha' min khlqh, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, falhlf bighayr allah shrk"
  37,5,"hw khaliq alsmwat wal'ard wama bynhma, wmdbbir alshams fi mtaleha wmgharbha"
  37,6,'inna zynna alsama' aldunya bizinat hi alnjwm
  37,7,whfzna alsama' bialnujum min kuli shaytan mtmrrid eat rjym
  37,8,"la tastatie alshayatin 'ana tasil 'iilaa almala alaela, wahi alsmwat wman fiha min almlaykt, ftstme 'iilayhim 'iidha tklmu bima ywhyh allah taealaa min shreh wqdrh, wyurjamwn balshhb min kuli jht; trdana lahum ean alastmae, walahum fi aldaar alakhirat eadhab dayim mwje"
  37,9,"la tastatie alshayatin 'ana tasil 'iilaa almala alaela, wahi alsmwat wman fiha min almlaykt, ftstme 'iilayhim 'iidha tklmu bima ywhyh allah taealaa min shreh wqdrh, wyurjamwn balshhb min kuli jht; trdana lahum ean alastmae, walahum fi aldaar alakhirat eadhab dayim mwje"
  37,10,"'ila man aikhtataf min alshayatin alkhtft, wahi alkalimat yasmaeha min alsama' bsret, fylqyha 'iilaa aldhy thth, wylqyha alakhar 'iilaa aldhy thth, frbma 'adrakah alshhab almudi' qabl 'an ylqyha, warubama 'alqaha bqadar allah taealaa qabl 'an yatih alshhab, fyhrqh fayadhhab biha alakhar 'iilaa alkhnt, fykdhbwn maeaha miayat kdhbt"
  37,11,"fasal -ayha alrswl- mnkry albaeth 'ahum 'ashadu khlqana 'am man khalaqna min hadhih almkhlwqat? 'iinaa khalaqna 'abahum adam min tin lzj, yltsq baedah bbed"
  37,12,"bl ejbt -ayha alrswl- min tkdhybhm w'inkarhm albeth, waejb min 'inkarhm wa'ablagh 'anahum yastahziuwn bk, wayaskharun min qwlk"
  37,13,w'idha dhkkiru bima nasuh 'aw ghafalu eanh la yntfewn bhdha aldhikr wala ytdbbarwn
  37,14,w'idha ra'awa mejzt dallat ealaa nbwwatk yskhrwn minha wyejbwn
  37,15,"wqalu: ma hdha aldhy jit bih 'iilaa sihr zahir byin. 'a'iidha mitna wsirna trabana wezamana bialyt 'a'iinaa lamabeuthun min qbwrna ahya', 'aw yubeth abawuna aladhin mdu min qblna?"
  37,16,"wqalu: ma hdha aldhy jit bih 'iilaa sihr zahir byin. 'a'iidha mitna wsirna trabana wezamana bialyt 'a'iinaa lamabeuthun min qbwrna ahya', 'aw yubeth abawuna aladhin mdu min qblna?"
  37,17,"wqalu: ma hdha aldhy jit bih 'iilaa sihr zahir byin. 'a'iidha mitna wsirna trabana wezamana bialyt 'a'iinaa lamabeuthun min qbwrna ahya', 'aw yubeth abawuna aladhin mdu min qblna?"
  37,18,"ql lahum -ayha alrswl-: nem sawf tubethwn, wa'antum adhla' saghrwn"
  37,19,"f'inma hi nafkhat wahdt, fa'iidha hum qayimun min qbwrhm yanzurun ahwal yawm alqyamt"
  37,20,"wqalu: ya hlakna hdha yawm alhisab waljza'"
  37,21,"fyqal lhm: hdha yawm alqada' bayn alkhalq bialeadl aladhi kuntum tukadhibun bih fi aldunya wtnkrwnh"
  37,22,"wyqal llmlaykt: ajmaeuu aladhin kafaruu biallah wnzra'hm walhthm alty kanuu yebdwnha min dun allh, fswqwhm swqana enyfana 'iilaa jhnm"
  37,23,"wyqal llmlaykt: ajmaeuu aladhin kafaruu biallah wnzra'hm walhthm alty kanuu yebdwnha min dun allh, fswqwhm swqana enyfana 'iilaa jhnm"
  37,24,"wahbswhm qabl 'an yasiluu 'iilaa jhnm; 'iinahum maswuwlun ean 'aemalihim waqwalhm alty sadarat eanhum fi aldnya, musa'alat 'inkar ealayhim wtbkyt lhm"
  37,25,"wyqal lahum twbykhana: ma lakum la yansur baedukum bedana?"
  37,26,"bl hum alyawm mnqadwn li'amr allh, la ykhalfwnh wala yhydwn enh, ghyr muntasirin lanfshm"
  37,27,waqbl bed alkufaar ealaa baed yatalawamun wytkhasmwn
  37,28,"qal alatbae llmtbweyn: 'iinakum kuntum tatunana min qibal aldiyn walhq, fthwwinwn ealayna 'amr alshryet, wtunaffirwnna enha, wtzynwn lana aldlal"
  37,29,"qal almtbwewn lltabeyn: ma al'amr kama tzemwn, bal kanat qulubikum munkirat ll'iyman, qabilat lilkufr walesyan"
  37,30,"wma kan lana ealaykum min hujat 'aw qwwat, fnsdkm biha ean al'iyman, bal kuntum -ayha almshrkwn- qwmana taghin mtjawzyn llhq"
  37,31,"flzimana jmyeana waeid rbna, 'iinaa ladhayiqu aledhab, nahn wantm, bima qadamna min dhunubana wmeasyna fi aldnya"
  37,32,"fadllnakm ean sabil allah wal'iiman bh, 'iinaa kunaa daliyn min qblkm, fhlkna; bsbb kfrna, wahlknakm mena"
  37,33,"fa'iin alatbae walmtbweyn mushtarikun yawm alqiamat fi aledhab, kama ashtrku fi aldunya fi mesyt allh"
  37,34,"'ina hkdha nafeal bialadhin akhtaru measy allah fi aldunya ealaa taeth, fndhyqhm aleadhab alalym"
  37,35,"'in 'uwlayik almushrikin kanuu fi aldunya 'iidha qil lhm: la 'ilh 'iilaa allh, wdeu 'ilyha, w'umru bitark ma ynafyha, yastakbirun eanha waealaa man ja' bha"
  37,36,"wyqwlwn: antrk eibadat alihatina laqawl rajul shaeir mjnwn? yenwn rasul allah salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  37,37,"kdhabu, ma muhamad kama wsfwh bh, bal ja' bialquran waltwhyd, wsddaq almursalin fima akhbru bih eanh min sharae allah wtwhydh"
  37,38,'inkm -ayha almshrkwn- bqwlkm wkfrkm wtkdhybkm ladhayiqu aleadhab al'alim almwje
  37,39,wma tujzawn fi alakhirat 'iilaa bima kuntum temlwnh fi aldunya min almeasy
  37,40,"'ila eibad allah taealaa aladhin akhlsu lah fi ebadth, fakhlshm wakhtshm brhmth; fa'iinahum najwn min aleadhab alalym"
  37,41,awlyk almkhlswn lahum fi aljanat rizq maelum la ynqte
  37,42,"dhlk alrizq fawakih mtnwet, wahum mukramun bkramt allah lahum fi janaat alnaeim aldaym"
  37,43,"dhlk alrizq fawakih mtnwet, wahum mukramun bkramt allah lahum fi janaat alnaeim aldaym"
  37,44,wmn kramthm eind rabihim w'ikram baeduhum bedana 'anahum ealaa surur mutaqabilin fima bynhm
  37,45,"ydar ealayhim fi mjalshm bkwws khamr min 'anhar jaryt, laa yakhafun anqtaeha, bayda' fi lwnha, ldhydht fi shrbha, lays fiha 'adhana lljsm wala lleql"
  37,46,"ydar ealayhim fi mjalshm bkwws khamr min 'anhar jaryt, laa yakhafun anqtaeha, bayda' fi lwnha, ldhydht fi shrbha, lays fiha 'adhana lljsm wala lleql"
  37,47,"ydar ealayhim fi mjalshm bkwws khamr min 'anhar jaryt, laa yakhafun anqtaeha, bayda' fi lwnha, ldhydht fi shrbha, lays fiha 'adhana lljsm wala lleql"
  37,48,"wendhm fi mjalshm nisa' efyfat, la ynzrn 'iilaa ghyr 'azwajahuna hisan alaeyn, ka'anahuna bayd mswn lm tmsh alaydy"
  37,49,"waeindahum fi mjalshm nisa' efyfat, la ynzrn 'iilaa ghyr 'azwajahuna hisan alaeyn, ka'anahuna bayd mswn lm tmsh alaydy"
  37,50,"faqbl bedhm ealaa bed yatasa'alun ean ahwalhm fi aldunya wama kanuu yueanun fyha, wama 'aneam allah bih ealayhim fi aljnt, whdha min tamam alans"
  37,51,"qal qayil min 'ahl aljnt: laqad kan li fi aldunya sahib mulazim ly"
  37,52,"yqwl: kayf tsddiq balbeth aldhy hu fi ghayat alastghrab? 'a'iidha mitna wtmzqna wsrna trabana wezamana, nubeth wnuhasb wnujaza baemalna?"
  37,53,"yqwl: kayf tsddiq balbeth aldhy hu fi ghayat alastghrab? 'a'iidha mitna wtmzqna wsrna trabana wezamana, nubeth wnuhasb wnujaza baemalna?"
  37,54,"qal hdha almumin aldhy 'udkhl aljanat lashabh: hal 'antum muttalewn linaraa masir dhlk alqryn? fatalae fraa qarinuh fi wasat alnar"
  37,55,"qal hdha almumin aldhy 'udkhl aljanat lashabh: hal 'antum muttalewn linaraa masir dhlk alqryn? fatalae fraa qarinuh fi wasat alnar"
  37,56,"qal almumin lqrynh almunkar llbeth: laqad qarbt 'ana thlkny bsdk 'iyay ean al'iiman law atetk. walawla fadl rabiy bhdayty 'iilaa al'iiman wtthbyty elyh, lakunt min almuhdarin fi aleadhab mek"
  37,57,"qal almumin lqrynh almunkar llbeth: laqad qarbt 'ana thlkny bsdk 'iyay ean al'iiman law atetk. walawla fadl rabiy bhdayty 'iilaa al'iiman wtthbyty elyh, lakunt min almuhdarin fi aleadhab mek"
  37,58,"ahqana 'anana mkhlladwn mneeamwn, fama nahn bimayitin 'iilaa mawtatana al'uwlaa fi aldnya, wama nahn bmedhdhabyn baed dkhwlna aljn? 'inn ma nahn fih min naeim lhu alzzafar alezym"
  37,59,"ahqana 'anana mkhlladwn mneeamwn, fama nahn bimayitin 'iilaa mawtatana al'uwlaa fi aldnya, wama nahn bmedhdhabyn baed dkhwlna aljn? 'inn ma nahn fih min naeim lhu alzzafar alezym"
  37,60,"ahqana 'anana mkhlladwn mneeamwn, fama nahn bimayitin 'iilaa mawtatana al'uwlaa fi aldnya, wama nahn bmedhdhabyn baed dkhwlna aljn? 'inn ma nahn fih min naeim lhu alzzafar alezym"
  37,61,"lmthl hdha alnaeim alkaml, walkhlwd aldaym, walfawz alezym, falyaemal aleamilun fi aldnya; lysyru 'iilayh fi alakhrt"
  37,62,"adhlk aldhy sabaq wasafah min naeim aljanat khayr dyaft weta' min allh, 'am shajarat alzaquwm alkhbytht almlewnt, taeam 'ahl alnar?"
  37,63,"'ina jaealnaha fitnatan afttn biha alzaalimun lanfshm bialkufr walmeasy, waqaluu mstnkryn: 'iina sahibukum yunabiyukum 'ana fi alnaar shjrt, walnaar takul alshjr"
  37,64,"'inha shajaratan tanbut fi qaer jhnm, thmrha qbyh almanzar ka'anah ruuws alshyatyn, fa'iidha kanat kdhlk fala tasal baed hdha ean temha, fa'iina almushrikin lakilun min tilk alshajarat famaliuwn minha btwnhm. thuma 'iinahum baed al'ukul minha lsharbwn shrabana khlytana qbyhana harrana, thuma 'iina mrddahm baed hdha aleadhab 'iilaa eadhab alnar"
  37,65,"'inha shajaratan tanbut fi qaer jhnm, thmrha qbyh almanzar ka'anah ruuws alshyatyn, fa'iidha kanat kdhlk fala tasal baed hdha ean temha, fa'iina almushrikin lakilun min tilk alshajarat famaliuwn minha btwnhm. thuma 'iinahum baed al'ukul minha lsharbwn shrabana khlytana qbyhana harrana, thuma 'iina mrddahm baed hdha aleadhab 'iilaa eadhab alnar"
  37,66,"'inha shajaratan tanbut fi qaer jhnm, thmrha qbyh almanzar ka'anah ruuws alshyatyn, fa'iidha kanat kdhlk fala tasal baed hdha ean temha, fa'iina almushrikin lakilun min tilk alshajarat famaliuwn minha btwnhm. thuma 'iinahum baed al'ukul minha lsharbwn shrabana khlytana qbyhana harrana, thuma 'iina mrddahm baed hdha aleadhab 'iilaa eadhab alnar"
  37,67,"'iinaha shajarat tanbut fi qaer jhnm, thmrha qbyh almanzar ka'anah ruuws alshyatyn, fa'iidha kanat kdhlk fala tasal baed hdha ean temha, fa'iina almushrikin lakilun min tilk alshajarat famaliuwn minha btwnhm. thuma 'iinahum baed al'ukul minha lsharbwn shrabana khlytana qbyhana harrana, thuma 'iina mrddahm baed hdha aleadhab 'iilaa eadhab alnar"
  37,68,"'inha shajaratan tanbut fi qaer jhnm, thmrha qbyh almanzar ka'anah ruuws alshyatyn, fa'iidha kanat kdhlk fala tasal baed hdha ean temha, fa'iina almushrikin lakilun min tilk alshajarat famaliuwn minha btwnhm. thuma 'iinahum baed al'ukul minha lsharbwn shrabana khlytana qbyhana harrana, thuma 'iina mrddahm baed hdha aleadhab 'iilaa eadhab alnar"
  37,69,"'inhm wajaduu aba'ahum ealaa alshirk waldlal, fsareu 'iilaa mtabethm ealaa dhlk"
  37,70,"'inhm wajaduu aba'ahum ealaa alshirk waldlal, fsareu 'iilaa mtabethm ealaa dhlk"
  37,71,wlqd dll ean alhaqu qabl qawmak -ayha alrswl- 'akthar al'umam alsabqt
  37,72,wlqd 'arsalna fi tilk al'umam mursilin andhrwhm bialeadhab fkfru
  37,73,"ftammal kayf kanat nihayat tilk al'umam alty andhrt, fkfrt? faqad eudhdhibt, wasarat lilnaas ebrt"
  37,74,"'ila eibad allah aladhin akhlshm allh, wkhssahm birahmatih l'ikhlashm lh"
  37,75,"wlqd nadana nbyna nwh; lnnsrh ealaa qwmh, falaniem almujibun lah nhn"
  37,76,"wnjynah wa'ahlah walmuminin maeah min 'adhaan almshrkyn, wamin algharaq baltwfan alezym"
  37,77,wjelna dhuriyatan nuh hum albaqin baed gharaq qwmh
  37,78,wabqyna lah dhikrana jamilana wthna'an hsnana fymn ja' baedah min alnaas ydhkrwnh bh
  37,79,"aman lnwh wslamt lah min 'an yudhkr bisu' fi alakhiryn, bal tuthny ealayh al'ajyal min bedh"
  37,80,mthl jaza'an nuh najzi kll man 'ahsan min aleabbad fi taeat allh
  37,81,'in nwhana min eibadina almusadiqin almukhlasin aleamilin bi'awamir allh
  37,82,"thm 'aghraqna alakharin almukadhibin min qawmih baltwfan, falam tbq minhum eayan tatrif"
  37,83,"w'inn min ashyae nuh ealaa mnhajh wmllath nby allah 'ibrahym, hin ja' rabah biqalb bari' min kuli aetqad batl wkhuluq dhmym, hin qal li'abih waqawmih mnkrana elyhm: ma aldhy tebdwnh min dun allh? 'aturidun alihatan mkhtlaqat tebdwnha, wttrkwn eibadat allah almsthq llebadt whdh? fama zanukum birabi alealamin 'anah faeil bikum 'iidha 'ashraktum bih webdtm maeah ghyrh?"
  37,84,"w'inn min ashyae nuh ealaa mnhajh wmllath nby allah 'ibrahym, hin ja' rabah biqalb bari' min kuli aetqad batl wkhuluq dhmym, hin qal li'abih waqawmih mnkrana elyhm: ma aldhy tebdwnh min dun allh? 'aturidun alihatan mkhtlaqat tebdwnha, wttrkwn eibadat allah almsthq llebadt whdh? fama zanukum birabi alealamin 'anah faeil bikum 'iidha 'ashraktum bih webdtm maeah ghyrh?"
  37,85,"w'inn min ashyae nuh ealaa mnhajh wmllath nby allah 'ibrahym, hin ja' rabah biqalb bari' min kuli aetqad batl wkhuluq dhmym, hin qal li'abih waqawmih mnkrana elyhm: ma aldhy tebdwnh min dun allh? 'aturidun alihatan mkhtlaqat tebdwnha, wttrkwn eibadat allah almsthq llebadt whdh? fama zanukum birabi alealamin 'anah faeil bikum 'iidha 'ashraktum bih webdtm maeah ghyrh?"
  37,86,"w'inn min ashyae nuh ealaa mnhajh wmllath nby allah 'ibrahym, hin ja' rabah biqalb bari' min kuli aetqad batl wkhuluq dhmym, hin qal li'abih waqawmih mnkrana elyhm: ma aldhy tebdwnh min dun allh? 'aturidun alihatan mkhtlaqat tebdwnha, wttrkwn eibadat allah almsthq llebadt whdh? fama zanukum birabi alealamin 'anah faeil bikum 'iidha 'ashraktum bih webdtm maeah ghyrh?"
  37,87,"w'inn min ashyae nuh ealaa mnhajh wmllath nby allah 'ibrahym, hin ja' rabah biqalb bari' min kuli aetqad batl wkhuluq dhmym, hin qal li'abih waqawmih mnkrana elyhm: ma aldhy tebdwnh min dun allh? 'aturidun alihatan mkhtlaqat tebdwnha, wttrkwn eibadat allah almsthq llebadt whdh? fama zanukum birabi alealamin 'anah faeil bikum 'iidha 'ashraktum bih webdtm maeah ghyrh?"
  37,88,"fnzr 'iibrahim nazratan fi alnujum mtfkrana fima yaetadhir bih ean alkhuruj maeahum 'iilaa aeyadhm, faqal lhm: 'iiniy mryd. whdha taerid mnh. ftrkwh wara' zhwrhm"
  37,89,"fnzr 'iibrahim nazratan fi alnujum mtfkrana fima yaetadhir bih ean alkhuruj maeahum 'iilaa aeyadhm, faqal lhm: 'iiniy mryd. whdha taerid mnh. ftrkwh wara' zhwrhm"
  37,90,"fnzr 'iibrahim nazratan fi alnujum mtfkrana fima yaetadhir bih ean alkhuruj maeahum 'iilaa aeyadhm, faqal lhm: 'iiniy mryd. whdha taerid mnh. ftrkwh wara' zhwrhm"
  37,91,"fmal msreana 'iilaa 'asnam qawmih faqal msthzyana bha: 'ala takulun hdha altaeam aldhy yuqadimuh lakum sdntkm? ma lakum la tantiqun wala tjybwn man ysalkm?"
  37,92,"fmal msreana 'iilaa 'asnam qawmih faqal msthzyana bha: 'ala takulun hdha altaeam aldhy yuqadimuh lakum sdntkm? ma lakum la tantiqun wala tjybwn man ysalkm?"
  37,93,faqbl ealaa alihatuhum ydrbha wykssirha biadih alymny; liuthabit liqawmih khataan ebadthm lha
  37,94,faqblu 'iilayh yaedun msreyn ghadbyn
  37,95,"flqyhm 'iibrahim bthbat qayla kayf taebudun asnamana tnhtwnha antm, wtsnewnha baydykm, wttrkwn eibadat rabakum aladhi khlqkm, wakhalaq emlkm?"
  37,96,"flqyhm 'iibrahim bthbat qayla kayf taebudun asnamana tnhtwnha antm, wtsnewnha baydykm, wttrkwn eibadat rabakum aladhi khlqkm, wakhalaq emlkm?"
  37,97,"(flma qamat ealayhim alhujat lajawuu 'iilaa alqw) wqalu: abnuu lah bnyanana wamlwwh htbana, thuma alqwh fyh"
  37,98,"fa'arad qawm 'iibrahim bih kydana l'ihlakh, fajaealnahum almqhwryn almghlwbyn, wrdd allah kaydahum fi nhwrhm, wajaeal alnnar ealaa 'iibrahim brdana wslamana"
  37,99,"wqal 'ibrahym: 'iiniy muhajir 'iilaa rabiy min balad qawmi 'iilaa hayth 'atamakan min eibadat rby; fa'iinah sydlny ealaa alkhayr fi diniin wdnyay. rabi aetny wldana salhana"
  37,100,"wqal 'ibrahym: 'iiniy muhajir 'iilaa rabiy min balad qawmi 'iilaa hayth 'atamakan min eibadat rby; fa'iinah sydlny ealaa alkhayr fi diniin wdnyay. rabi aetny wldana salhana"
  37,101,"fajbna lah dewth, wbshsharnah bighulam hlym, ay: yakun hlymana fi kbrh, wahu 'ismaeyl"
  37,102,"flma kabir 'iismaeil wmsha mae 'abih qal lah abwh: 'iiniy 'araa fi almanam 'aniy adhbhk, fama rayk? (wrwya al'anbia' hq) faqal 'iismaeil murdyana rbh, barrana bwaldh, meynana lah ealaa taeat allh: amd ma amrk allah bih min dhbhy, satajiduni -'in sha' allh- sabrana tayeana mhtsbana"
